Model weights, datasets, and hardware/CAD files
--------------------------------------------------

No pretrained model weights (`*.pt`), training datasets, or hardware/CAD
files are committed to this repository (see `.gitignore`: `weights/`,
`*.pt`, `weights_config.json`, `openvino_model_cache/`). YOLO weight files
referenced by the application are downloaded at runtime from Ultralytics'
own distribution channels under Ultralytics' licensing terms (AGPL-3.0,
as noted above) and are not redistributed as part of this repository. If
Roboflow-sourced or other third-party datasets are added to this
repository in the future, their license/attribution terms (e.g. Roboflow
datasets are frequently CC BY 4.0, which requires attribution) must be
recorded here before distribution.
